## TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS

### Stack
- **Framework:** Next.js 15 (App Router) — or React + Vite if simpler
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4 + CSS variables for the design token layer
- **Animations:** Framer Motion for entrance animations + hover states
- **Icons:** Lucide React (line-art, consistent weight)
- **Fonts:** Google Fonts via `next/font` (DM Serif Display + Instrument Serif + Sora)
- **Images:** `next/image` with proper `alt` text. Use `object-fit: cover` for portrait

### Component Architecture

```
/components
  /layout
    Navbar.tsx          — sticky, blur-on-scroll
    Footer.tsx
  /sections
    Hero.tsx
    TrustBar.tsx
    Services.tsx        — card grid + coming soon badges
    FounderStory.tsx
    ValuesGrid.tsx
    MissionVision.tsx
    BrandMoment.tsx     — typographic ilmu × mundo section
    CTA.tsx
  /ui
    SectionLabel.tsx    — reusable "SERVICES" caps label
    ServiceCard.tsx     — available now card
    ComingSoonBadge.tsx — pill badge
    ValueCard.tsx
    PullQuote.tsx
    CTAButton.tsx       — primary + ghost variants
```

### Responsive Behavior
- Mobile-first. Everything works at 375px.
- Hero: stacked, headline smaller but still impactful
- Services: single column cards
- Founder: portrait above, text below
- Navigation: hamburger → full-screen overlay, large type, centered

### Accessibility
- Semantic HTML: `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, `<article>`, `<footer>`
- All images: descriptive `alt` text
- Color contrast: minimum 4.5:1 for body text
- `prefers-reduced-motion`: disable all animations
- Focus states: visible, styled with brand color ring

### Performance
- Fonts: `display: swap`, preload critical fonts
- Images: WebP, lazy load below fold
- Animations: CSS `transform` + `opacity` only (no layout thrashing)
- No animation library loaded unless actually used

---

## WHAT MAKES THIS PREMIUM (CHECKLIST)

Before you ship, verify:

- [ ] No Inter, Roboto, or system font in sight
- [ ] Cream warm background — never pure `#FFFFFF`
- [ ] Section headers are large, bold serif — not SaaS sans-serif
- [ ] Cards feel physical: subtle shadow, real radius, white surface on colored bg
- [ ] Section color blocks have `border-radius: 28px` and side margins
- [ ] Service brand names (Antero, Didik, UNIk etc.) are typographically celebrated, not hidden
- [ ] Pullquotes are large, italic serif — editorial, not testimonial widget
- [ ] "ilmu · mundo" brand moment section is a design pause — no clutter
- [ ] Footer social row is icon-only, tight, clean
- [ ] Every hover state is defined and intentional
- [ ] Mobile nav is full-screen, large type — not a hamburger dropdown
- [ ] Animations feel editorial (slow, graceful) — not playful (bouncy, fast)
- [ ] No purple gradients, no glassmorphism abuse, no floating blob shapes

---

## TONE OF VOICE (for any copy you write)

- **Confident, not arrogant** — "We know what works" not "We're the best"
- **Warm, not casual** — formal enough for parents, approachable enough for students
- **Specific, not vague** — "7 global cities" not "international experience"
- **Malaysian-proud, not provincial** — celebrate the roots, don't apologize for them
- **Short sentences. Active voice. Serif soul.**

---

## REFERENCE SITES (study these before building)

- **craft.do** — section color blocks, card layouts, pullquote styling, footer structure
- **linear.app** — dark sections, motion, premium SaaS editorial feel
- **framer.com** — hero energy, typography scale, CTA treatment
- **loom.com** — founder-forward storytelling, warm brand feel

---

*Build this like you're shipping for a client who will show it to investors. Every pixel should earn its place.*